# Vercel Speed Insights Installation Report

## Summary
Vercel Speed Insights was **already installed and configured** in this project. No changes were necessary.

## Verification Steps Completed

1. ✅ **Fetched Latest Documentation**: Retrieved the official Vercel Speed Insights quickstart guide from https://vercel.com/docs/speed-insights/quickstart to ensure we follow the most up-to-date installation instructions.

2. ✅ **Identified Framework**: Confirmed this is a Next.js 14.2.25 project using npm as the package manager.

3. ✅ **Package Installation**: Verified `@vercel/speed-insights` version ^2.0.0 is present in package.json dependencies and package-lock.json.

